> 
> flush(stderr()); flush(stdout())
> 
> ### Name: NiftiExtensionCodes
> ### Title: Known NIfTI Extension Codes
> ### Aliases: NiftiExtensionCodes
> ### Keywords: datasets
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> # Get the code for AFNI extensions
> NiftiExtensionCodes["AFNI"]  # Returns 4
AFNI 
   4 
> 
> # Get the name for a code
