> ### Name: which_dim
> ### Title: Find Dimensions of a Given Axis
> ### Aliases: which_dim which_dim,NeuroSpace,NamedAxis-method
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> 
> x <- NeuroSpace(c(10,10,10), spacing=c(1,1,1))
> which_dim(x, x@axes@j) == 2
[1] TRUE
